WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.040 --> 00:00:10.050
If you haven't been to the Disneyland Resort
lately, prepare to be amazed!

00:00:10.050 --> 00:00:13.520
There's so much to see and do from day to
night for the whole family, you'll need multiple

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:15.090
days to enjoy it all.

00:00:15.090 --> 00:00:18.529
Here are some magical travel tips to help
you plan a 3-day visit.

00:00:18.529 --> 00:00:23.020
First, book a Hotel &amp; Ticket Package that
includes a stay at one of the hotels at the

00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:24.400
Disneyland Resort.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:29.540
The resort benefits allow more time for family
fun and the amenities make it an unforgettable

00:00:29.540 --> 00:00:31.790
storybook vacation.

00:00:31.790 --> 00:00:36.230
Benefits include Extra Magic Hours, which
lets you enjoy early admission to select attractions

00:00:36.230 --> 00:00:40.110
at one of the Disneyland Theme Parks everyday
of your stay.

00:00:40.110 --> 00:00:44.010
There's also a special entrance into Disney
California Adventure Park.

00:00:44.010 --> 00:00:49.150
Plus, you're just steps away from Downtown
Disney District, an eclectic shopping, dining

00:00:49.150 --> 00:00:51.140
and entertainment district.

00:00:51.140 --> 00:00:54.940
Amenities include Disney-themed Resort rooms,
pools and water-play areas.

00:00:54.940 --> 00:00:58.090
You can even schedule a Disney character wake-up
call.

00:00:58.090 --> 00:01:03.520
Staying at the Resort makes it easy to return
to your hotel during the day for a quick break,

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:06.110
swim, maybe even a spa treatment.

00:01:06.110 --> 00:01:10.170
When you're ready for adventure, head over
to the recently expanded Disney California

00:01:10.170 --> 00:01:11.170
Adventure Park.

00:01:11.170 --> 00:01:15.820
Buckle up for fun on Radiator Springs Racers
at Cars Land.

00:01:15.820 --> 00:01:19.200
Catch the entertaining vibe happening on Buena
Vista Street.

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:22.400
Light up the night with the dazzling World
of Color Water Spectacular.

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:27.070
While you're at the Theme Parks, remember
to take advantage of Disney's FastPass service

00:01:27.070 --> 00:01:28.710
on select attractions.

00:01:28.710 --> 00:01:32.880
It's included with a valid Theme Park admission
that lets you enjoy the Disneyland Resort

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.060
while your place in line is saved.

00:01:35.060 --> 00:01:40.390
Of course your vacation isn't complete without
a visit to the one and only, original Disneyland

00:01:40.390 --> 00:01:41.940
Park.

00:01:41.940 --> 00:01:48.460
Step into Fantasy Faire, an enchanting storybook
world where "Happily ever after" happens every

00:01:48.460 --> 00:01:49.460
day.

00:01:49.460 --> 00:01:52.140
Revisit timeless favorites like Matterhorn
Bobsleds.

00:01:52.140 --> 00:01:57.380
Blast off with over 50 possible adventures
on Star Tours -- The Adventures Continue.

00:01:57.380 --> 00:02:00.810
Rock the night with fireworks!

00:02:00.810 --> 00:02:04.750
You can find wait times for popular attractions
posted in front of the Jolly Holiday Bakery

00:02:04.750 --> 00:02:06.689
CafÃ© on Main Street, U.S.A.

00:02:06.689 --> 00:02:12.590
Or, you can view approximate wait times on
your mobile device by going to M.Dinseyland.Com.

00:02:12.590 --> 00:02:17.079
As you can see, the Disneyland Resort is now
bigger, better and more magical than ever

00:02:17.079 --> 00:02:18.079
before.

00:02:18.079 --> 00:02:19.149
We hope to see you here real soon!

